    <lb n="1"/>ὅ<unclear>π</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ω</supplied><unclear>ς</unclear> μὴ διὰ τὸ τῆς χαρᾶς τῆ<supplied reason="lost">ς</supplied> ἑα<unclear>υτ</unclear>ῶν <choice><reg>δήλωσ<supplied reason="omitted">ιν</supplied></reg><orig>δηλως</orig></choice> ποιήσασθαι <choice><reg>ἐθέλειν</reg><orig>ἐ<unclear>θ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">έ</supplied><unclear>λ</unclear>ιν</orig></choice>, ἣν ἐπʼ ἐμοὶ παρελθόντι ἐπὶ τὴν ἀρχὴν 

